msgctxt "80_Akiyama"
msgid "Honestly, I didn't expect you to do this well."
msgstr "Sinceramente, no esperaba que lo hicieras tan bien."

msgctxt "92_Shiobara"
msgid "Please, a loss is a loss... But I guess I did do pretty\\r\n"\n"well, didn't I?"
msgstr "Una derrota es una derrota, no hace falta decorarla...\\r\n"\n"Pero lo hice bastante bien a pesar de todo, ¿no cree?"

msgctxt "104_Akiyama"
msgid "Absolutely."
msgstr "Absolutamente."

msgctxt "116_Akiyama"
msgid "When it comes down to it, the trick is in fulfilling\\r\n"\n"customers' needs over and over against practically\\r\n"\n"miraculous odds."
msgstr "Al final, el truco está en cumplir con lo que los\\r\n"\n"clientes quieren una y otra vez, aunque conseguirlo\\r\n"\n"parezca un milagro."

msgctxt "128_Akiyama"
msgid "In fact, it's pretty much the ideal sales model."
msgstr "De hecho, es la forma ideal de hacer negocios."

msgctxt "140_Akiyama"
msgid "By quickly feeling out the locals' needs and supplying just\\r\n"\n"the right goods, you wound up with a very valuable prize."
msgstr "Al comprender las necesidades locales y proveer los\\r\n"\n"productos adecuados, obtuviste un artículo muy valioso."

msgctxt "152_Akiyama"
msgid "You've got a pretty good knack for business, if you ask me."
msgstr "En mi opinión, posees un talento nato para los negocios."

msgctxt "164_Shiobara"
msgid "Is that what you were trying to test?"
msgstr "¿Estabas tratando de comprobar eso con la prueba...?"

msgctxt "176_Akiyama"
msgid "One of the things, anyway."
msgstr "Bueno, supongo que era una de las razones."

msgctxt "188_Shiobara"
msgid "...I don't get you, Akiyama-san. You always seem like you're\\r\n"\n"just goofing around, then, next thing I know, you zero in on\\r\n"\n"something profound like that..."
msgstr "...No te entiendo, Akiyama-san. Siempre pareces estar\\r\n"\n"bromeando, pero la realidad es que detrás de esa\\r\n"\n"fachada hay algo más profundo de lo que aparenta..."

msgctxt "200_Akiyama"
msgid "You overestimate me. Mostly I just say whatever comes to\\r\n"\n"mind."
msgstr "Lo estás exagerando un poco. Usualmente solo digo lo que\\r\n"\n"pienso en el momento."

msgctxt "212_Shiobara"
msgid "No, you really are special. I'm glad I was able to do as\\r\n"\n"well as I did against an opponent like you."
msgstr "No, realmente eres increíble. Estoy orgulloso de haberlo\\r\n"\n"hecho tan bien contra un rival como tú..."

msgctxt "224_Shiobara"
msgid "...I almost feel like I could start over."
msgstr "...Siento que podría intentarlo de nuevo."

msgctxt "236_Shiobara"
msgid "I may be down, but I'm not out! I did all this with a single\\r\n"\n"cigarette－and I can do more!"
msgstr "¡Estar sin dinero es lo máximo! Logré llegar hasta acá con\\r\n"\n"un simple cigarrillo... ¡Imagina las posibilidades!"

msgctxt "248_Akiyama"
msgid "There's that twinkle in your eye!"
msgstr "¡Esa mirada tuya lo dice todo!"

msgctxt "260_Shiobara"
msgid "Thank you, Akiyama-san. I knew I was drawn back to this part\\r\n"\n"of town for a reason－it was to see you!"
msgstr "Gracias, Akiyama-san. Al final, creo que volví inconscientemente\\r\n"\n"a la ciudad, solo para volver a encontrarme contigo."

msgctxt "272_Shiobara"
msgid "Be on the lookout for me! I just know I'm going to make it\\r\n"\n"big again one day!"
msgstr "¡El mundo aún no ha visto lo mejor de mí, volveré a la cima!\\r\n"\n"¡Ya lo verás!"

msgctxt "284_Akiyama"
msgid "Yeah. Counting on it."
msgstr "Espero con ansias ver eso."

msgctxt "296_Shiobara"
msgid "Thanks! See you!"
msgstr "¡Gracias! ¡Nos vemos!"

msgctxt "320_Akiyama"
msgid "Shiobara?"
msgstr "Shiobara."

msgctxt "332_Shiobara"
msgid "Yes?"
msgstr "¿Sí?"

msgctxt "344_Akiyama"
msgid "Here. You forgot this."
msgstr "Ten. Olvidaste esto."

msgctxt "380_Shiobara"
msgid "Oof! Did you have to throw it? I can't think of anything\\r\n"\n"I've forg..."
msgstr "¡Ay! ¿Por qué lo lanzaste?\\r\n"\n"No recuerdo haber olvidado..."

msgctxt "392_Shiobara"
msgid "Huh!? It's money."
msgstr "¡¿Eh?! ¿Esto no es dinero?"

msgctxt "404_Akiyama"
msgid "Yep. Five million, to be exact."
msgstr "En efecto. Cinco millones, para ser exactos."

msgctxt "416_Shiobara"
msgid "But why?"
msgstr "Pero, ¿por qué?"

msgctxt "428_Akiyama"
msgid "I lent you five million and you insisted on returning ten\\r\n"\n"million."
msgstr "Te presté cinco millones y te empeñaste en devolverme\\r\n"\n"diez millones."

msgctxt "440_Akiyama"
msgid "\"No interest, no collateral.\" Hasn't that sunk in yet?"
msgstr "¿No te lo he repetido más de una vez? Sin intereses."

msgctxt "452_Akiyama"
msgid "That money is yours."
msgstr "Ese dinero de ahí, es tuyo."

msgctxt "464_Shiobara"
msgid "Akiyama-san..."
msgstr "Akiyama-san..."

msgctxt "476_Akiyama"
msgid "Just promise me one thing. My customers never come back for\\r\n"\n"seconds."
msgstr "Y recuerda lo otro. Mis clientes nunca vuelven a pedirme\\r\n"\n"prestado dinero."

msgctxt "488_Akiyama"
msgid "Either they fail the test and leave angry, or they pass the\\r\n"\n"test and change their lives forever. One of the two."
msgstr "O fallan la prueba y se marchan furiosos, o bien la superan\\r\n"\n"y sus vidas cambian para siempre. Una de las dos."

msgctxt "500_Akiyama"
msgid "It would be a real shame if my apprentice wound up being my\\r\n"\n"very first repeat customer."
msgstr "Sería una vergonzoso que mi aprendiz termine siendo\\r\n"\n"mi primer cliente recurrente."

msgctxt "512_Shiobara"
msgid "...Right! I'll do my very best!"
msgstr "... ¡Entiendo! ¡Me esforzaré al máximo!"

msgctxt "524_Akiyama"
msgid "Later!"
msgstr "¡Hasta luego!"

